column5: I caught this fish on a canoe trip this summer, wondering what you guys think its weight is, im 6'3" for reference.
I would say maybe somewhere around 4 pounds.
I'd be more concerned with the ghost behind you.
Will your fist fit in its mouth? If not its not 5 lbs.
LOL! I was about to say the same.
3 if your arm is extended, 4.1 if it is not
